te. They may not be able to be displayed or edited correctly, once you have removed this content type.','none'),(2809,'','default','If the site is experiencing problems with permissions to content, you may have to rebuild the permissions cache. Possible causes for permission problems are disabling modules or configuration changes to permissions. Rebuilding will remove all privileges to posts, and replace them with permissions based on the current modules and settings.','none'),(2810,'','default','Rebuilding may take some time if there is a lot of content or complex permission settings. After rebuilding has completed posts will automatically use the new permissions.','none'),(2811,'','default','Node access status','none'),(2812,'','default','Number of posts on main page','none'),(2813,'','default','The default maximum number of posts to display per page on overview pages such as the main page.','none'),(2814,'','default','Are you sure you want to rebuild the permissions on site content?','none'),(2815,'','default','This action rebuilds all permissions on site content, and may be a lengthy process. This action cannot be undone.','none'),(2816,'','default','Demote from front page','6.26'),(2817,'','default','Make sticky','6.26'),(2818,'','default','Remove stickiness','6.26'),(2819,'','default','language','6.26'),(2820,'','default','An error occurred and processing did not complete.','none'),(2821,'','default','Show summary in full view','6.26'),(2822,'','default','The trimmed version of your post shows what your post looks like when promoted to the main page or when exported for syndication.<span class=\"no-js\"> You can insert the delimiter \"&lt;!--break--&gt;\" (without the quotes) to fine-tune where your post gets split.</span>','none'),(2823,'','default','Copy of the revision from %date.','none'),(2824,'','default','@type %title has been reverted back to the revision from %revision-date.','none'),(2825,'','default','Revision from %revision-date of @type %title has